[150]. Copyright 2020, Elsevier. c Diagram of the passivation mechanism. d Fabrication procedure for perovskite solar cells by R2R process. eJ-V curves of flexible devices (1.01 cm2) with and without HI treatment. Inset presents the photograph of flexible perovskite solar cells. f Normalized PCE of encapsulated PSCs based on NiOx and NiOx (HI) hole-transport layers under ambient condition (25–55% relative humidity and 25–35 ℃) for 30 days. c-f Reproduced with permission from Ref. [146]. Copyright 2021, Royal Society of Chemistry2.2-10(CH3NH3)PbI3+Ni≥3+Ox↔Ni≥2+OxH+PbI2+CH3NH2↑+12I2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
